HEADWORD: Apricate
<hw>Ap"ri*cate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>apricatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>apricare</ets>, fr.
<ets>apricus</ets> exposed to the sun, fr. <ets>aperire</ets> to
uncover, open.]</ety> <def>To bask in the sun.</def>
